dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Benjamin Nelson. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Nicole! Can you please provide me with the year your car was manufactured and the number of miles on its odometer?
My car was manufactured in two zero one five, and it has sixty-five thousand three hundred miles on it.
Thank you for that information, Nicole. To further assist you, could you also share the number of years you've been with Old Stone Auto Insurance and your current policy number?
I've been with Old Stone Auto Insurance for three years now, and my policy number is five six two eight one zero.
Great. Thank you, Nicole, for providing those details. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No, I think that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Nicole. If you have any further questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
